 offer multi-functional travel gear that gets you to and from your destination with durable function and uncompromised style. Want to buy the best luggage brand bags? Think eBags.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Travel Gear</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\">Planning a trip? Visit eBags travel store for your must buy travel bag and accessories. Flying by plane? Choose from the best carry-on luggage available that fits the airlines specifications and size. Hiking? Purchase durable camping gear; strong tents, sleeping bags, and a hiking backpack from brands like Swissgear and The Northface. eBags was started by pioneers and takes pride in continuing to spearhead innovative solutions across all demographics. Thinking travel? Think eBags.</p>',NULL,'rich_text_box',17,'Home'),(23,'site.facebook_url','Facebook Url','https://www.facebook.com/balo153/',NULL,'text',20,'Site'),(24,'site.youtube_url','Youtube Url','https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFyZUWZGBzBHxl5URzbcgsg?view_as=subscriber',NULL,'text',21,'Site'),(25,'site.twitter_url','Twitter Url','https://twitter.com/balo153',NULL,'text',27,'Site'),(26,'site.feed_url','Feed url',NULL,NULL,'text',28,'Site'),(27,'footer.description','Site Description','<img src=\"/storage/settings/July2018/IVSjpgZOCBoNOIlZilWc.jpg\"/>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Up to 10% back on every Order.</li>\r\n    <li>Exclusive member savings.</li>\r\n    <li>Easy access to order tracking &amp; history.</li>\r\n    <li>It\'s FREE.</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'code_editor',22,'Footer'),(28,'payment-methods.cash_description','Cash Description','<p>Thanh to&aacute;n khi nhn h&agrave;ng cho giao nhn.&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'rich_text_box',24,'Payment Methods'),(29,'payment-methods.transfer_description','Bank Transfer Description','<p>Vui l&ograve;ng chuyn khon n t&agrave;i khon:</p>\r\n<p><strong>VIETCOMBANK</strong>: 0123457891000</p>\r\n<p><strong>ACB</strong>: 01